#### Structs

##### `Item`

Kitchen sink struct exercising every field feature

Passed as opaque handle (`i64`).

| Accessor | WASM Return |
|----------|-------------|
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_id` | `i64` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_name` | `i32, i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_count` | `i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_enabled` | `i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_ratio` | `f64` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_nick` | `i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_payload` | `i32, i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_tags` | `i32, i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_attrs` | `i64` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_parent` | `i32, i32` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_token` | `i64` |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_get_priority` | `i32` |

##### `ItemBuilder`

Builder for `Item`.

