|----------|------|--------|
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_new` | none | `i32` (handle) |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_id` | `i32` handle, `i64` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_name` | `i32` handle, `i32, i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_count` | `i32` handle, `i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_enabled` | `i32` handle, `i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_ratio` | `i32` handle, `f64` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_nick` | `i32` handle, `i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_payload` | `i32` handle, `i32, i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_tags` | `i32` handle, `i32, i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_attrs` | `i32` handle, `i64` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_parent` | `i32` handle, `i32, i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_token` | `i32` handle, `i64` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_set_priority` | `i32` handle, `i32` value | none |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_build` | `i32` handle | `i32` (handle) |
| `weaveffi_kitchen_Item_Builder_destroy` | `i32` handle | none |

#### Enums

##### `Priority`

Task priority levels

Passed as `i32` discriminant.

| Variant | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `Low` | `0` |
| `Normal` | `1` |
| `High` | `2` |
